---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Mountain Wedding Invitations | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Mountain wedding invitation suites inspired by alpine scenery, forest venues, outdoor ceremonies, national park weddings, and nature-inspired design.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Mountain Wedding Invitations</h1>

    <p>
      Alpine views, forest details, natural textures, and outdoor-inspired design.
      Our mountain wedding invitation suites are inspired by scenic landscapes,
      evergreen forests, national parks, rustic lodges, and romantic outdoor ceremonies.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you are planning a mountain lodge wedding, forest ceremony, national park
      elopement, or destination wedding surrounded by nature, these invitation suites
      are designed to feel elevated, organic, and connected to place.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Inspired by Scenic Outdoor Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      Mountain weddings are known for dramatic views, natural beauty, and a strong
      sense of place. These invitation suites often feature landscape-inspired layouts,
      evergreen details, earthy color palettes, refined rustic typography, topographic
      accents, and nature-inspired design elements.
    </p>

    <p>
      Popular wedding venues and settings for this style include mountain lodges,
      ski resorts, forest venues, lakeside ceremonies, national parks, ranches,
      cabins, and destination weddings in scenic outdoor locations.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular Mountain Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Mountain wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Forest wedding invitation suites</li>
      <li>National park wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Rustic mountain wedding stationery</li>
      <li>Evergreen wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Alpine wedding invitation designs</li>
      <li>Lodge wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Outdoor wedding stationery</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Designed for Nature-Inspired Celebrations</h2>

    <p>
      Our mountain invitation suites are created for couples who want their wedding
      stationery to reflect the beauty of their venue and destination. Each suite can
      include save the dates, wedding invitations, RSVP cards, details cards,
      welcome signage, menus, seating charts, and day-of wedding stationery.
    </p>

    <p>
      We focus on cohesive wedding branding that connects your invitation suite with
      your setting, your style, and your wedding day experience.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom Mountain Wedding Stationery</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for a fully custom design? We can create personalized mountain wedding
      invitation suites based on your venue, scenery, color palette, typography
      preferences, trail-inspired details, map elements, and overall wedding aesthetic.
    </p>

    <p>
      From elevated rustic designs to clean nature-inspired layouts, we help create
      wedding stationery that feels thoughtful, scenic, and unique to your celebration.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>What is a mountain wedding invitation style?</h3>
    <p>
      Mountain wedding invitations are inspired by alpine scenery, forests, outdoor
      venues, lodge details, earthy colors, and nature-focused design. The style can
      feel rustic, elegant, adventurous, or refined.
    </p>

    <h3>Are mountain wedding invitations good for national park weddings?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Mountain-inspired invitation suites work well for national park weddings,
      forest ceremonies, lake weddings, lodge celebrations, and outdoor destination events.
    </p>

    <h3>Can you include custom maps or location details?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Custom map elements, venue details, travel information, and weekend itinerary
      cards can be designed as part of the invitation suite.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching wedding day stationery?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching welcome signs, menus, seating charts, place cards, and other
      day-of stationery can be created to match your invitation suite.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
